## 4. Session Pitfalls (Complete Log)
=========================================

1. PATH: GHC/cabal installed via ghcup but not on default PATH
   Fix: export PATH="$HOME/.ghcup/bin:$PATH"

2. cabal update concurrency: Multiple cabal update processes ran simultaneously
   Fix: Killed stale processes, ran single update

3. zlib build failure: Two concurrent builds tried to install zlib simultaneously
   Fix: Killed competing processes, retried clean build

4. Auth bypass bug (CRITICAL): All handlers used flawed 'unless (evaluate ...) $ pure $ errorResponse ...'
   The 'unless' discarded the error Response, continuing to execute the operation
   Fix: Rewrote all handlers to use 'if not (evaluate ...) then pure errorResponse else do ...'

5. WAI Query type mismatch: 'lookup "prefix" q' returns 'Maybe (Maybe ByteString)', handlers expected 'Maybe Text'
   Fix: Wrote 'lookupQuery' helper with join + decodeUtf8'

6. XML compilation cascade: X.emptyNode not exported, elementChildren not found, nodeContent not found
   Fix: Replaced X.emptyNode with mempty, wrote childElements + textContent helpers, used X.qualified record fields

7. Double replace disaster: Global '[]' → 'mempty' corrupted [Node] lists
   Fix: Rewrote XML.hs from scratch with correct Element constructor usage

8. Agent-induced import issues: Subagent added unnecessary deps (case-insensitive, resourcet, http-types)
   Conduit types changed to require MonadResource, transPipe liftIO, etc.
   Fix: Accept the working state, cleanup will happen in lint phase

9. Test OverloadedStrings: 3 test files missing LANGUAGE pragma
   Fix: Added {-# LANGUAGE OverloadedStrings #-} to PolicySpec, XMLSpec, SigV4Spec

10. Test LambdaCase: XMLSpec used \case without LambdaCase extension
    Fix: Added {-# LANGUAGE LambdaCase #-}

11. Data.ByteArray import: Test suite didn't have 'memory' package in deps
    Fix: Simplified SigV4Spec to not need Data.ByteArray

12. Stale background builds: Multiple cabal build processes accumulated
    Fix: Killed and restarted clean

13. pre-commit-lint skill updated mid-session: Added "build with warnings" requirement
    Impact: Can't commit until 31 warnings + hlint are fixed

14. errorResponse duplication: Same 5-line function in 5 different modules
    Fix pending: Move to XML.hs as single source of truth

